high_descs: turn right walk across room, turn right walk until you reach table
turn around walk until you reach refrigerator
place cup in refrigerator to cool, take cup out of refrigerator
turn around walk toward the table
place cup back on coffee maker

high_descs: Turn to your right head to the table on your right
Pick up the cup on the coffee maker
Turn around to your right walk to the fridge then open the two door fridge
Put the cup on the right side of the door fridge then close them again
Turn around to your right and go back to the table
Put the cup back to the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the cup on the fridge, going back to the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn right, head to the door, turn right, head to the table.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Turn around and bring the mug to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Take out the chilled mug, turn around and bring the mug back to the table.
Put the chilled mug on the coffee machine on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the coffee machine.
